														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2389170">
									

<p>Ignoring the meat of the article for the moment, I was surprised by this for one reason. When we think about Foundation personnel, we think about doctors in sites, studying contained anomalies and coming up with ways to contain them better. We think about MTF crews, out in the field, hunting monsters. But time and again, articles will mention embedded agents, in governments, businesses, organizations and subcultures the world over. That's a lot of personnel, and we never hear their stories.</p>
<p>So that whetted my appetite and the payoff was absolutely worth it. :D This is great.</p>

