														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2389493">
									

<p>No, it's not an SCP. Actually it's a reference to the movie &quot;2001: A Space Odyssey&quot; where in the end we see a &quot;space child&quot; whith its mysterious crystal eyes. I tried to express this idea: the astronaut, a &quot;Son of Earth&quot;, turns from familiar, terrestrial, warm things to the cold unknown Space. To the Great Unknown. And after this moment he is no longer a Son of Earth, he is reborn and becomes a Child of Space.</p>

							</div>

								
